{"tid":511633,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日去見工 樣衰到嚇到hr叫保安","createTime":"2017-12-27T16:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:26:14.000Z","uid":31887,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a7806045b285c4044a8f23456521e09c622613","tid":511633,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日去見份文員工<br />\n我坐底之後hr個八婆問我點稱呼<br />\n我話我叫師父哥（我個名諧音）<br />\n跟住佢西左我面講 吓？<br />\n以為佢聽唔到咁我重複多句<br />\n係師父哥呀經理<br />\n唔講由至可 一講塊面仲黑撚過黑鮑<br />\n可能我個名加左個哥字佢唔like<br />\n我心諗吳業坤都叫坤哥啦<br />\n咁我醒水 即刻補飛話自己叫師父<br />\n屌拿星 佢即刻串鳩我話我咁既工作經驗學人叫師父<br />\n咁我都假假地ive大學畢業<br />\n我即刻反佢枱屌佢係低學力廢柴 字都唔識一隻學人咁串<br />\n當場屌佢老母 問佢知唔知咩叫莫欺少年窮<br />\n跟住我就比保安拖左出去<br />\n如果我生得係靚仔一定唔會發生呢件事"},{"pid":"82945b0a78650f9bcfcb457356ea19537ff8517b","tid":511633,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"c8dc9055cdd775d8786a8554d3d2de6d33ec093e","tid":511633,"uid":77985,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，浪費我人生20秒"},{"pid":"02760353f353d31de452f801aa22352f3736bc91","tid":511633,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母，浪費我人生20秒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbef5048f60ac5be44514439ce970433f7800291","tid":511633,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T18:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ff43f04b1c04a888f6b2749eedcbf1cf9c834f","tid":511633,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:26:14.000Z","msg":"Haha"}]}